The core project depends on the following libraries: 

* python-dateutil: convert any date-string into datetime object
* redis and pyredis: shared memory and cache between fetching of the whois and core of the program
* IPy: all manipulations on the IP addresses
* elixir and sqlalchemy: Active record
* feedparser: parse the rss files 

The website depends on: 

* cherrypy: server 
* Cheetah: templates

The code is currently only tested with Python 2.6 and should not work with Python 3.X. Python 3.X will be supported till all used dependency support Python 3.X.